delines due to their high potency and low resistance of the virus.3,4Although entecavir has a high genetic barrier to resistance, resistance to entecavir has been reported with a significant incidence rate, especially in patients with genotypic resistance to lamivudine and a prior history of lamivudine treatment.5,6
