gnificant increase in mortality risk.18However, the deleterious impact of NSBBs in patients with advanced cirrhosis remains a controversial issue.Indeed, several studies did not find any association between NSBBs and increased mortality in patients with ascites while, in some series, outcome was found to be better in patients receiving NSBBs, suggesting that only a subset of these patients could be at risk.19–22
